::KitKat::

She looked up at Phobia with tear stained cheeks. "He's gone.  I..I 
couldn't save him. I tried to, but he didn't make it."  She stood up 
and looked at Phobia with tears running down her face.  This was the 
first time she had ever faced death like this.  It scared her to see 
someone that she had known, die in her arms like that. She hoped that 
it would never happen again. But knew that one day, it might.
